Zero Hangover

1. Use Drink List to select drink or add new drinks
2. Hit "Start" 
3. Press a button for corresponding drink when you drink it 
4. Fewer stars indicates an estimated worse hangover 
5. When finished drinking, hit "Stop" 
6. The next morning, rate how you feel 

The app will save the rating and adjust the measurements for the next use. The more you use it, the more accurate it will be able to estimate how you will feel the next day.